{"tid":458133,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打會因為個女仔唔係處而唔同佢一齊?","createTime":"2017-11-04T14:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T09:11:57.000Z","uid":21097,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb2d44d9c27c88104064f4bdbb0b856f03217de","tid":458133,"uid":21097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:25:20.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打會因為個女仔唔係處而唔同佢一齊?<br />\n(假設本身你地真係有機會喺埋一齊)<br />\n你係點發現條女唔係處? 或者點開口問佢係咪處?"},{"pid":"2bf7ab2847a00fdadee5718801c45da62f23a5bc","tid":458133,"uid":5806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:44:59.000Z","msg":"最緊要坦白 同埋相愛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53b3972ffec5c3234b83547d56cf81b05f2ab89","tid":458133,"uid":21097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要坦白 同埋相愛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係接納佢?"},{"pid":"f85f4a5fabee3e842cbc2f2aff5605800d943fe9","tid":458133,"uid":88521,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"個陣同條女一齊第一日佢坦白同我講左佢唔係<br />\n我係真係有一刻想分手 因為自己思想好守舊  但我調番轉諗其實真係愛大家就算啦<br />\n過左去既野 做左都無得彌補 咪唯有叫佢好好對我"},{"pid":"c0fe9ba30e9c7b537969ccb262a25a712c893323","tid":458133,"uid":21097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個陣同條女一齊第一日佢坦白同我講左佢唔係<br />\n我係真係有一刻想分手 因為自己思想好守舊  但我調番轉諗其實真係愛大家就算啦<br />\n過左去既野 做左都無得彌補 咪唯有叫佢好好對我</blockquote><br />\n但個心唔會一直都有條刺咩？"},{"pid":"6cd612bb12e1f24a54bb6a48b5b8beb94549ce59","tid":458133,"uid":74262,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:19:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c22fe89bef0931637952bd8a93d38e09b8b424c5","tid":458133,"uid":74262,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a9083aa8802190ac38bc071f674d1a553014a75","tid":458133,"uid":83998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:24:57.000Z","msg":"曾經都有處女情意結<br />\n但當你遇到個值得對佢好 想保護佢既人個時<br />\n自然唔到你介意"},{"pid":"1e6ae4d42713c8a1ec44f25ff071db883a400881","tid":458133,"uid":88521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個陣同條女一齊第一日佢坦白同我講左佢唔係<br />\n我係真係有一刻想分手 因為自己思想好守舊  但我調番轉諗其實真係愛大家就算啦<br />\n過左去既野 做左都無得彌補 咪唯有叫佢好好對我</blockquote><br />\n但個心唔會一直都有條刺咩？</blockquote><br />\n有一定有既 但好多野都好難講<br />\n啱對方 大家相處得開心 就唔會點去計<br />\n雖然我係在意"},{"pid":"a8033627b49f5c4de39a260a37f8b9bc59f8ed78","tid":458133,"uid":81214,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:26:04.000Z","msg":"當然有 中出即飛<br />\n再搵過件處"},{"pid":"3145cc16a58d032939874c23b5fdd60b16898e4c","tid":458133,"uid":88521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個陣同條女一齊第一日佢坦白同我講左佢唔係<br />\n我係真係有一刻想分手 因為自己思想好守舊  但我調番轉諗其實真係愛大家就算啦<br />\n過左去既野 做左都無得彌補 咪唯有叫佢好好對我</blockquote><br />\n但個心唔會一直都有條刺咩？</blockquote><br />\n因為佢知道佢已經冇能力搵返一個條件咁好/比佢好既女 <br />\n所以就接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你靚仔有事業 結局一定唔係咁</blockquote><br />\n係呀 你最靚仔 又有事業 去揾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又無人阻你 希望你揾到"},{"pid":"37287fb46c32e065319d283207f019fadbfc81c5","tid":458133,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:31:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c48881c460facf33202747654a4f4b921710c574","tid":458133,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:49:02.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n屌住先"},{"pid":"a54b4930b59f3ed373d8d67d8165985e81d3fad8","tid":458133,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T00:52:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會<br />\n屌住先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯,遇到處嘅先換"},{"pid":"3e07f7e2699af586afc3de98e911c4bc35c7bb93","tid":458133,"uid":11496,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T02:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個陣同條女一齊第一日佢坦白同我講左佢唔係<br />\n我係真係有一刻想分手 因為自己思想好守舊  但我調番轉諗其實真係愛大家就算啦<br />\n過左去既野 做左都無得彌補 咪唯有叫佢好好對我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解佢唔係處好似欠左你咁 仲要好好對你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ad413da27e34adb0a64a27e0a512e9b2bf31e7","tid":458133,"uid":106390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:37:35.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n我都仲考慮緊 睇下巴打意見"},{"pid":"673a869212a56f2d6c36e8325391d223ba49fc57","tid":458133,"uid":74262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c5ce74c3bcb2881ea3952bcca404224b3d5fadb","tid":458133,"uid":106390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>LM<br />\n我都仲考慮緊 睇下巴打意見</blockquote><br />\n咁介意人地目光既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算你條女係咪處 你都係廢男人</blockquote><br />\n先唔講我想睇下其他巴點做選擇係咪等於我介意人目光<br />\n<br />\n但係介意人目光同係咪廢男人邏輯上有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：唔想引戰 純粹想睇下連登仔係咪會因為唔係處就乜乜物物"},{"pid":"060ca4457b8e6307c883accb867dfa76107dc16c","tid":458133,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"773b34f96bb9112f4b70bb5262b9ec685f9253ac","tid":458133,"uid":5921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T07:50:52.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為個post係小多士開"},{"pid":"f8a3b4ff98027a40bb026adcee73d0b35bb6d8bd","tid":458133,"uid":21097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c8f26733d8e8079d3b5bfdb04f6604afacffee2e","tid":458133,"uid":21097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"如果自己係處, 但條女唔係呢?"},{"pid":"5be7e6add7388b15cdd23bb85aff4382ce1275d7","tid":458133,"uid":119399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime